Restoration Plots Audit

Chris Beirne

2024-06-21

Forest Restoration Plots

The aim of this document is to present Planet Labs with all the locations we have performed restoration.

The following maps represent the landowners properties where we have performed such activities. IMPORTANT POINT these are not the areas planted!

I used the shapefiles provided by the restoration team in this folder.

I have split these files into:

  1. Farms for Nature (farms4nature)

  2. Planting planned for this year (planned) - may also include locations planted in previous years

  3. Locations planted in previous years - 2020 to 2023 (planted)

  4. Abandonned - we are no longer working with these landowners

Biodiversity surveys

An important element of this was to check if the biodiversity surveys are also occurring in the places where restoration is occuring. Below I overlay the survey locations provided by the Wildlife team in this folder.

It seems like four of the locations I don’t have polygons for. Maybe we no longer work with those land owners?

RF29 - Sonia Aragon (near Agua Buena)

RF19 - Vilma Garcia (near Colorado) [ I think coordinates just need adjusting slightly]

RF20 - Irvin Rodriguez (near La Lucha)

Resolved RF12 - Tulio Coopesabalito (near Sabalito) [Land owner discontinued]
